invocation.excerpt:
Copy your images (xxx.jpg) to /images. 
Command: python run_demo.py 
Copy configs/detector_coco.py to ./detector.py 
Copy configs/train_coco_2x.json to ./train.json 
Configure train.json file, add your root.
Average Precision  (AP) @[ IoU=0.75      | area=   all | maxDets=100 ] = 0.398

Copy configs/detector_voc.py to ./detector.py 
Copy configs/train_voc.json to ./train.json 
Configure train.json file, add your root.  
Command: python run_train.py  to start schedule.

Create data_eval.txt (same format as data_train.txt) 
Config train.json file, add your root.
